# 默认：文本文件按内容自动判定，统一使用 LF 行尾。
# 覆盖 Windows 上 core.autocrlf=true 导致的 CRLF，避免与 Prettier endOfLine=lf 冲突。
* text=auto eol=lf

# 明确标记二进制资源，防止 git 误判并禁止 EOL 转换。
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.eot binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.so binary
*.dylib binary
*.wasm binary
